0.9.0.name: wordpress/empty-paragraph-for-tinymce-editor
0.9.0.description: This is a very simple plugin for the default (TinyMCE) editor. It adds a button that puts in a paragraph which won't get deleted by the linebreak-eater (the one that starts munching when you press "Publish").
